    "If multiple obstacles are at the same distance, one is randomly selected to define P ĵ.S j (t) = H, T, P ĵ ∈ R 2(N +M +1)(8)The control input of herder j is sampled from a (possibly stochastic) decentralized policy conditioned on its observation:u j (t) ∼ π( • | S j (t)), j = 1,..., N.(9)The control objective is achieved if∃ t g < +∞ s.t.",
